Text: Ladda inte ner denna, den är, genom dålig, inte för att jag förvänta mig mycket utifrån basmaterialet.
Ska inte parodi vara roligt detta är ju bara skräp.

Well, this can be kinda funny, if you're danish. The reason being that the swedish language is so absurd to danes that words like "knulla" is hilarious in themselves.
That is pretty much the same reason why anybody listens to the original in Denmark - for a cheap laugh. 
Also the poor quality is an ironic comment on the quality of the original - which is pretty damned bad.

It's not my song and I don't necessarily find it particularly amusing but I uploaded it for those who might. If it's not your thing you don't have to listen to it again. :)
